Native Instruments - FM8 v1.3.0 - AU.RTAS.VST.ST - OS X [packet-dada]
303.9 MB

Minumum System OS X 10.7

Snow Leopard: Extract with Pacifist and replace old Plugins
Standalone .app Change Info.plist Minimum System Version 10.7.0 to 10.6.8 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.3

What's new:
- Advanced integration in MASCHINE 2.0 host software

Fixes:
- Chunk re-call of certain FM8 sounds broken.
- Parameters in Easy / Morph Mode not recalled correctly.
- Easy / Morph page automation issues.
- Crashes while deleting a point of an envelope.
- Browser response laggy.
- Cannot type into the microtuning preset box.
- Preset name of FM matrix not updating.
- Misc. minor fixes.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Install FM8 v1.3.0

Dellete .plist

Macintosh HD /Library/Preferences/com.native-instruments.FM8.plist
Macintosh HD /Users/Library/Preferences/com.native-instruments.FM8.plist

Replace all CRACKS files to default Dir.

Replace Plugins

Applications  /Applications/Native instruments/FM8
Plugins Dir (AU/VST/RTAS/)

OPEN FIRST STANDALONE VERSION!

Enjoy!
